## Create the data source that will link Red Dog and the database

One way to do that is by adding the following tag to `<GlobalNamingResources>` in `$CATALINA_HOME/conf/server.xml`, and replacing the dummy values:

	<Resource name="jdbc/rdap"
	    type="javax.sql.DataSource"
	    auth="Container"
	    driverClassName="com.mysql.jdbc.Driver"
	    url="[mydb_url]"
	    username="[mydb_user]"
	    password="[mydb_pass]"
	    validationQuery="select 1 from dual" />

